headline: S&P 500, Nasdaq Jump. Most Chip Stocks Are Higher, Too.
summary: The stock market jolted higher shortly after the open as much of the tech universe, including semiconductor stocks, sees aggressive buying.  The S&P 500 was up 1%, while the Dow rose 0.4%.  Both indexes had declined for four straight days coming into today's session.

headline: Bailard Completes Three Strategic Property Acquisitions in Q3
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, November 19, 2025--The Bailard Real Estate Fund completed three acquisitions in key U.S. markets during the third quarter of 2025, marking a deliberate return to active capital deployment. With select opportunities emerging as pricing adjusts and fundamentals stabilize, the Fund continues to invest through a disciplined, process-driven lens, focusing on properties that can generate income today and value over time.

headline: Is Tutor Perini Still Worth a Look After 150% Rally and New Contracts in 2025?
summary: Thinking about investing in Tutor Perini? Let’s dig into whether the stock’s current price truly offers value, or if the market’s excitement is already included in the price. After a huge rally this year with the share price up 150.3% year-to-date and an incredible 106.0% jump over the past twelve months, Tutor Perini has quickly become a hot topic among growth-focused investors.
